# backend/presenter_router.py
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Unified presenter — formats ANY structured data into the
# envelope format that the frontend RenderBlock component expects.
#
# KEY DESIGN:
#   - Tables are built LOCALLY by _flatten_top_level() — NO LLM.
#   - Summaries are generated by the shared llm.py gateway
#     (same provider/model the rest of the app uses).
#   - PII is stripped from data BEFORE it reaches the LLM.
#   - The frontend envelope contains the ORIGINAL (full) data.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
